window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Still reeling from betrayal, Reality’s newest sorcerer finds herself at the heart of a centuries-old conspiracy that could destabilize worlds.</b></p> <p>Billions of lives are at risk. Hidden motivations are everywhere. Evander has family trouble. Lennu has a theory. Gale has gossip—doesn’t she always? And Kira has a plan. Maybe. If her magic would just behave.</p> <p>Join the House in the thrilling conclusion to the&nbsp;Uncertain Sanctuary&nbsp;series. Science fantasy at its startling, genre-bending best.</p>"; 
